                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "The village is dying, Anne. I need to know if there's any way to stop it."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "Stop it? You mean the infection? There's a lab. Sarah was working on something before she... well, before she got sick."
