                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "You need the lab key. Old George might know where it ended up, or maybe you'll find it in the graveyard. But first, you need to get the power back on."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "And the power?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "George handles the grid. But he needs a fuse. I heard there's one inside the lab. It's a catch-22, isn't it?"
