                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "I have the antidote, Sarah. I'm ready to use it."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "sarah",
                    "line": "Do it. Please. The pain is... it's hard to think clearly."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Hold on."
